      "body" : "NACK. I think the code should exist for people to use for testing, but I dont think Bitcoin Core is the place to support a ton of test/benchmark chains. This is different from the regtest/testnet chains, which exist to create a bitcoin-in-a-box for testing, but which try to mimic Bitcoin where convinient for testing, not to test changes to Bitcoin itself.",
